    actor U as Utente
    participant V as Vista (TheoremPage)
    participant C as Controller (useGraphSandboxStore)
    participant UT as Utility (graphUtils)
    participant DB as Database (ContentDAO)

    U->>V: Clicca "Attiva Assioma"
