    DB-->>C: GraphStructure (Entity)
    C->>UT: evaluateActiveGraph(activeAxioms, GraphStructure)
    Note over UT: Algoritmo di<br/>Ordinamento Topologico
    UT-->>C: Set~String~ validNodes
    C->>C: Crea GraphEvaluationDTO
    C-->>V: Invia GraphEvaluationDTO
